      "para_id": "Q004931.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) Šu-Suen , the powerful man , king of Urim , king of the four quarters : Urmeme , the gardener of Enlil , child of Niĝ-dugani , the gardener of Enlil , is your servant ."
